CREATED:20260227T191834Z
DESCRIPTION:Set aside time and space to focus on your writing as we welcom
 e spring. Retreat includes structured writing time in a supportive commun
 ity\, opportunities to connect with other writers\, and an optional works
 hop on cultivating a sustainable writing practice. Open to faculty in any
  discipline. The retreat cohort will include writers from different disci
 plines and career stages. \n\nNote: Retreat is full. Waitlist-only regist
 ration.
DURATION:PT7H
