DESCRIPTION:Graduate Liberal Studies Information Sessions for prospective 
 students\, which last about an hour\, are the best way to learn more abou
 t the Master of Arts in Liberal Studies degree at Duke University.\n\nThe
 se sessions\, held online on Zoom every other Friday morning throughout t
 he academic year\, provide the opportunity to meet GLS staff who will tal
 k in-depth about the program and answer your questions. GLS staff members
  will discuss degree requirements\, the application and admissions proces
 s\, and financial assistance.
DURATION:PT1H
