CREATED:20260202T144201Z
DESCRIPTION:Are you a Duke student working on a startup\, building a techn
 ology\, or exploring an idea you want to keep moving forward? The Christe
 nsen Center is hosting Founders Fridays\, a monthly\, open mentoring sess
 ion for student founders during the Spring 2026 semester.\n\nFounders Fri
 days is an informal "Ask Us Anything" space where you can get feedback\, 
 advice\, and support on whatever you're working on-from early ideas to ac
 tive ventures. Members of the Christensen Center leadership team will be 
 there to help you think through challenges\, next steps\, and opportuniti
 es\, while also connecting with other student founders.\n\nAll students a
 re welcome\, and no RSVP is required. Just drop in!
DURATION:PT1H
DTSTAMP:20260202T144201Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260306T110000
LAST-MODIFIED:20260202T144201Z
