DESCRIPTION:Learn about the history\, architecture\, and life of Duke Chap
 el on this tour\, which is free and open to the public.\n\nThe tour begin
 s at 12:15 p.m.\, or immediately following the conclusion of the Sunday m
 orning service\, and lasts approximately forty-five minutes. No reservati
 on is required\, but if you plan to bring a large group\, please notify u
 s in advance. Meet the docent on the front steps of the Chapel.\n\nPaid p
 arking is available on a first-come\, first-served basis in the Bryan Cen
 ter Parking Lot at 125 Science Drive. ADA parking is available in the Bry
 an Center Surface Lot at the same address.
DURATION:PT1H
